1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,290
[Episode 57]

2
00:00:02,290 --> 00:00:04,970
-Let me order.
-Please go ahead.

3
00:00:09,710 --> 00:00:12,970
-Hello, I'd like two truffle pastas.
-Sure.

4
00:00:12,970 --> 00:00:16,490
And two Caesar salads with smoked salmon.

5
00:00:16,490 --> 00:00:18,530
-Alright. Anything else?
-No, that's all.

6
00:00:18,530 --> 00:00:19,730
To go, please.

7
00:00:19,730 --> 00:00:20,370
Sure.

8
00:00:20,370 --> 00:00:21,570
To go.

9
00:00:22,490 --> 00:00:23,730
Ah, why?

10
00:00:25,410 --> 00:00:26,930
Isn't Bin coming?

11
00:00:27,170 --> 00:00:30,050
No. He doesn't want to see anyone right now.

12
00:00:30,050 --> 00:00:32,450
Especially you two.

13
00:00:32,729 --> 00:00:35,490
So what should we do?

14
00:00:36,250 --> 00:00:38,380
Who's this 'we' you're talking about?

15
00:00:38,770 --> 00:00:41,290
In this situation,

16
00:00:41,290 --> 00:00:47,010
I'm afraid only I can heal his wounded heart.

17
00:00:48,050 --> 00:00:50,850
Then why waste time meeting here?

18
00:00:51,570 --> 00:00:53,050
Taji.

19
00:00:55,410 --> 00:00:56,490
Stop right there.

20
00:00:56,490 --> 00:00:59,330
If you make this big guy put a black plastic bag over my head again,

21
00:00:59,330 --> 00:01:03,490
I swear I'll be the first to convince Bin to kick you out.

22
00:01:04,250 --> 00:01:08,890
What if his friends can't heal him? What should we do?

23
00:01:10,450 --> 00:01:14,810
Are you deaf? There is no 'we' here.

24
00:01:16,930 --> 00:01:19,170
If that's really the case,

25
00:01:19,170 --> 00:01:23,850
I'll definitely support my friend finding someone new. As for you guys,

26
00:01:25,770 --> 00:01:30,410
Look, there's a secondhand shop over there. You might still fetch some money.

27
00:01:30,810 --> 00:01:35,080
Drew, I'm not joking. I came here today to talk to Bin.

28
00:01:35,810 --> 00:01:37,930
Go get Bin to see me now.

29
00:01:38,170 --> 00:01:42,050
Max, you need to stop controlling everyone around you,

30
00:01:42,050 --> 00:01:43,810
especially those you love.

31
00:01:43,810 --> 00:01:45,250
As for you, Fuzhi,

32
00:01:45,570 --> 00:01:51,610
It's okay. If Bin isn't ready to see me, I'll go find him myself.

33
00:01:54,360 --> 00:02:00,480
-Hey, wait!
-Hey, volcano man!

34
00:02:01,530 --> 00:02:05,690
As for you, pay for my meal. Consider it compensation for my wasted time.

35
00:02:07,370 --> 00:02:08,729
Taji, take care of it.

36
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:14,440
[To Be Continued]
